rComments: This is an instructor that truly cares for his students, despite his strict appearance. His exams are designed solely to test one's understanding of the course's fundamentals. Out of the 8 quizzes, the best 4 were taken, accounting for 20% of the final mark. Labs are designed to provide practical insight of the course. Highly recommended :)
